Title: How To Throw A Party
Book Description: 'The panelists have thrown many great parties over the years - join them for conversations on how to be a good host- creating atmosphere- and maintaining energy. Bring your own best tips and great party stories.'

Title: Dirty Tricks Swordfighting
Book Description: 'In a real swordfight- you want as many as you can get.  At Aegis Consulting- it's just another practice.'

Title: One Deep Breath: Psychology in Fighting
Book Description: 'Explore the impact of psychology in combat.'

Title: Board-Breaking Class
Book Description: 'A fundamental feat of confidence and will- board breaking is one of the first- most dramatic tests of Eastern martial arts.  Join Aegis as we teach you what it takes for you to break a board or two. Take your broken board home with you as proof or your new prowess!'

Title: Sneak Like Ninja, Move With Grace
Book Description: 'A class on balance- grounding- and silent walking.'

Title: War of Ideas: Promoting Change
Book Description: 'Direct conflict is only one manner of affecting the world.  This discussion focuses on the multitude of tactics for the creating social improvement.'

Title: Archetypes in Modern Culture
Book Description: 'Joseph Campbell's 'Hero With a Thousand Faces' tells the tale of the Tale: the archetypal path of life.  What kind of a Hero are you? Where in your Quest are you? How does the concept of the Archetype in you impact your day to day?'
